<!DOCTYPE html><html lang="uk"><head><meta charset="UTF-8"><meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"><title>Календар освітлення + </title><link rel="icon" href="data:image/svg+xml,<svg xmlns=%22http://www.w3.org/2000/svg%22 viewBox=%220 0 100 100%22><text y=%22.9em%22 font-size=%2290%22>🌙</text></svg>"><link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Outfit:wght@300;400;500;600;700&family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet"><style>:root{--bg:#0d0f14;--surface:#151820;--surface2:#1c2030;--border:#4F4255;--border-cell:#4F4255;--accent-on:#f5a623;--accent-off:#4a9eff;--accent-on2:#ff6b35;--text:#e8eaf0;--text-dim:#a0a8b8;--text-muted:#6b7280;--success:#2ecc71;--danger:#e74c3c;--highlight-last-opened:#AFB1B8;--highlight-pasted:#4a9eff;--highlight-edited:#29B766}*{box-sizing:border-box;margin:0;padding:0}body{background:var(--bg);color:var(--text);font-family:Outfit,sans-serif;min-height:100vh;overflow-x:hidden;user-select:none}header{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#0d0f14,#151c2e);border-bottom:2px solid var(--border);padding:5px 8px;position:sticky;top:0;z-index:100}.header-top{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;margin-bottom:4px}.file-btn{background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--accent-on),var(--accent-on2));color:#000;border:none;border-radius:7px;padding:5px 6px;font-size:18px;cursor:pointer;flex-shrink:0;line-height:1}.save-btn{background:var(--surface2);border:1px solid var(--success);color:var(--success);border-radius:7px;padding:5px 8px;font-size:16px;cursor:pointer;flex-shrink:0;line-height:1;display:none}.save-btn.show{display:block}.file-info{font-size:15px;color:#c8d0e0;font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;word-break:break-all;line-height:1.3;flex:1;text-align:center;overflow:hidden;display:-webkit-box;-webkit-line-clamp:2;-webkit-box-orient:vertical;cursor:pointer;border-radius:6px;padding:1px 3px}.file-info:active{background:rgba(255,255,255,.05)}#fileInput{display:none}.nav-row{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:4px;flex-wrap:wrap}.nav-btn{background:var(--surface2);border:1px solid var(--border);color:var(--text);border-radius:7px;width:32px;height:32px;font-size:15px;cursor:pointer;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;flex-shrink:0}.month-label{background:var(--surface2);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:7px;font-size:15px;font-weight:600;text-align:center;flex:1;padding:5px 4px;cursor:pointer;line-height:1.3}.month-label:active{opacity:.7}.nav-spacer{flex:0 0 7px}.ch-btns{display:flex;gap:2px;flex-shrink:0}.ch-btn{background:var(--surface2);border:1px solid var(--border);color:#c8d0e0;border-radius:6px;padding:4px 8px;font-family:Outfit,sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-weight:600;cursor:pointer;transition:.15s}.ch-btn.active{background:#c37c09;border-color:var(--accent-on);color:#000}.dst-spacer{flex:0 0 7px}.dst-btn{background:var(--surface2);border:1px solid var(--border);color:#c8d0e0;border-radius:6px;padding:4px 8px;font-size:14px;cursor:pointer;transition:.15s;flex-shrink:0}.dst-btn.active{background:#2a5298;border-color:#4a7fd4}.weekdays{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(7,1fr);gap:10px;margin-top:5px;border-top:1px solid var(--border);padding-top:8px}.weekday{text-align:center;font-size:12px;font-weight:600;color:#8890a0;text-transform:uppercase}#mainContent{overflow:hidden;position:relative;touch-action:pan-x pan-y pinch-zoom}.calendar-wrap{padding:3px 5px}.calendar-wrap.slide-from-right{animation:.28s cubic-bezier(.25,.8,.35,1) calSlideFromRight}.calendar-wrap.slide-from-left{animation:.28s cubic-bezier(.25,.8,.35,1) calSlideFromLeft}@keyframes calSlideFromRight{from{transform:translateX(28%);opacity:0}to{transform:translateX(0);opacity:1}}@keyframes calSlideFromLeft{from{transform:translateX(-28%);opacity:0}to{transform:translateX(0);opacity:1}}.days-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(7,1fr);gap:2px;align-items:stretch}.day-cell{background:var(--surface);border:1px solid var(--border-cell);border-radius:8px;padding:3px 2px;cursor:pointer;display:flex;flex-direction:column}.day-cell:active{opacity:.8}.day-cell.empty{background:0 0;border-color:transparent;cursor:default}.day-cell.today{border-color:var(--accent-on);background:var(--bg)}.day-cell.last-opened{outline:1px dashed var(--highlight-last-opened);outline-offset:1px}.day-cell.no-data .day-num{opacity:.25}.day-cell.no-data .events{visibility:hidden}.day-cell.virtual-day{border-style:dashed}.day-cell.virtual-day .day-num{color:#6b7280}.day-num{font-size:12px;font-weight:600;color:var(--text);margin-bottom:2px;line-height:1;display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center}.day-cell.today .day-num span{color:var(--accent-on)}.events{display:grid;gap:1px;flex:1}.event-chip{border-radius:3px;padding:1px 2px;font-size:12px;font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-weight:600;white-space:nowrap;line-height:1.4;min-height:18px;text-align:center;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center}.chip-empty{border-radius:3px;background:0 0;visibility:hidden}.chip-on{color:var(--accent-on);background:rgba(245,166,35,.12)}.chip-off{color:var(--accent-off);background:rgba(74,158,255,.1)}.chip-more{font-size:11px;font-weight:700;color:#c8d0e0;padding:1px 2px;text-align:center;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center}.empty-state{display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;justify-content:center;padding:60px 20px;gap:16px;text-align:center}.empty-icon{font-size:52px}.empty-title{font-size:18px;font-weight:600}.empty-sub{font-size:13px;color:var(--text-dim);line-height:1.5;max-width:260px}.upload-big-btn{background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--accent-on),var(--accent-on2));color:#000;border:none;border-radius:12px;padding:13px 26px;font-family:Outfit,sans-serif;font-weight:700;font-size:15px;cursor:pointer;margin-top:8px}.hide-load-buttons .file-btn,.hide-load-buttons .upload-big-btn{display:none!important}.modal-overlay{display:none;position:fixed;inset:0;background:rgba(0,0,0,.7);z-index:200;align-items:flex-end;backdrop-filter:blur(4px)}.modal-overlay.show{display:flex}.modal{background:var(--surface);border-radius:20px 20px 0 0;border-top:1px solid var(--border);width:100%;padding:20px;max-height:85vh;display:flex;flex-direction:column;animation:.25s slideUp}@keyframes slideUp{from{transform:translateY(100%)}to{transform:translateY(0)}}.modal-handle{width:36px;height:4px;background:var(--border);border-radius:2px;margin:0 auto 16px;flex-shrink:0}.modal-title{font-size:18px;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:14px;color:var(--accent-on);display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:8px;flex-shrink:0}.modal-events-scroll{flex:1;overflow-y:auto;margin-bottom:16px}.modal-event{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px;padding:10px 0;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border)}.modal-event:last-child{border-bottom:none}.modal-event-time{font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:24px;font-weight:500;min-width:90px}.modal-event-label{font-size:16px;color:#c8d0e0}.modal-event-badge{margin-left:auto;padding:4px 12px;border-radius:20px;font-size:13px;font-weight:600}.badge-on{background:rgba(245,166,35,.2);color:var(--accent-on)}.badge-off{background:rgba(74,158,255,.15);color:var(--accent-off)}.modal-close{width:100%;padding:12px;background:var(--surface2);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:10px;color:var(--text);font-family:Outfit,sans-serif;font-size:17px;font-weight:500;cursor:pointer;flex-shrink:0}.save-day-btn{display:none;background:var(--success);color:#000;border:none;padding:12px;border-radius:10px;font-weight:600;font-size:16px;cursor:pointer;flex:1}.modal-buttons-row{display:flex;gap:8px;margin-top:16px;flex-shrink:0}.modal.edit-mode .modal-event{padding:8px 0}.modal.edit-mode .modal-event-time{font-size:20px}.modal.edit-mode .modal-event-label{font-size:14px}.modal.edit-mode .modal-event-badge{font-size:12px}.modal.edit-mode .modal-close{flex:1;width:auto}.modal.edit-mode .save-day-btn{display:block}.modal.edit-mode .time-separator{font-size:24px}.modal.edit-mode .edit-event-hours,.modal.edit-mode .edit-event-minutes{font-size:24px;width:55px}.modal.edit-mode .edit-event-type{font-size:15px;padding:6px 18px}.modal.edit-mode .delete-event-btn{font-size:15px;padding:6px 10px}.modal.edit-mode .add-event-hours,.modal.edit-mode .add-event-minutes{font-size:20px;width:48px}.modal.edit-mode .add-event-type-toggle{font-size:15px;padding:6px 20px}.modal.edit-mode .add-event-title{font-size:13px;margin-bottom:8px}.modal.edit-mode .add-event-controls{gap:10px}.time-separator{font-size:28px;font-weight:500;margin:0 2px;color:var(--text-dim)}.edit-event-time-container{display:flex;align-items:center;background:var(--surface2);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:10px;padding:4px 8px}.edit-event-hours,.edit-event-minutes{font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:28px;font-weight:500;width:65px;text-align:center;background:0 0;border:none;color:var(--text);padding:4px 0}.edit-event-hours:focus,.edit-event-minutes:focus{outline:0}.edit-event-time-container.on{border-color:var(--accent-on);background:rgba(245,166,35,.1)}.edit-event-time-container.on .edit-event-hours,.edit-event-time-container.on .edit-event-minutes{color:var(--accent-on)}.edit-event-time-container.off{border-color:var(--accent-off);background:rgba(74,158,255,.08)}.edit-event-time-container.off .edit-event-hours,.edit-event-time-container.off .edit-event-minutes{color:var(--accent-off)}.edit-event-type{font-size:16px;font-weight:600;cursor:pointer;padding:8px 20px;border-radius:10px;transition:.1s;border:none}.edit-event-type.on{background:rgba(245,166,35,.2);color:var(--accent-on)}.edit-event-type.off{background:rgba(74,158,255,.15);color:var(--accent-off)}.delete-event-btn{background:rgba(231,76,60,.15);border:1px solid var(--danger);color:var(--danger);border-radius:8px;padding:8px 12px;cursor:pointer;font-size:16px;margin-left:auto}.add-event-section{background:var(--surface2);border-radius:16px;padding:12px 16px;margin-top:16px;flex-shrink:0}.add-event-title{font-size:14px;font-weight:600;margin-bottom:10px;color:var(--accent-on)}.add-event-controls{display:flex;gap:12px;align-items:center;flex-wrap:wrap}.add-event-time-container{display:flex;align-items:center;background:var(--bg);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:10px;padding:4px 8px}.add-event-time-container.on{border-color:var(--accent-on);background:rgba(245,166,35,.1)}.add-event-time-container.on .add-event-hours,.add-event-time-container.on .add-event-minutes{color:var(--accent-on)}.add-event-time-container.off{border-color:var(--accent-off);background:rgba(74,158,255,.08)}.add-event-time-container.off .add-event-hours,.add-event-time-container.off .add-event-minutes{color:var(--accent-off)}.add-event-hours,.add-event-minutes{font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:24px;font-weight:500;width:55px;text-align:center;background:0 0;border:none;color:var(--text);padding:4px 0}.add-event-hours:focus,.add-event-minutes:focus{outline:0}.add-event-type-toggle{font-size:16px;font-weight:600;padding:8px 24px;border-radius:10px;cursor:pointer;transition:.1s;border:none}.add-event-type-toggle.on{background:rgba(245,166,35,.2);color:var(--accent-on)}.add-event-type-toggle.off{background:rgba(74,158,255,.15);color:var(--accent-off)}.add-event-submit{background:rgba(46,204,113,.15);border:1px solid var(--success);color:var(--success);border-radius:8px;padding:8px 16px;cursor:pointer;font-size:18px;font-weight:600;margin-left:auto}.format-dialog-overlay{display:none;position:fixed;inset:0;background:rgba(0,0,0,.8);z-index:400;align-items:center;justify-content:center}.format-dialog-overlay.show{display:flex}.format-dialog{background:var(--surface);border-radius:20px;padding:24px;width:280px;text-align:center;border:1px solid var(--border)}.format-dialog-title{font-size:18px;font-weight:600;margin-bottom:16px}.format-dialog-buttons{display:flex;gap:12px;justify-content:center;margin-top:20px}.format-btn{padding:10px 20px;border-radius:10px;font-weight:600;cursor:pointer;border:none}.format-btn.lc{background:var(--accent-on);color:#000}.format-btn.txt{background:var(--accent-off);color:#000}.format-btn.cancel{background:var(--surface2);border:1px solid var(--border);color:var(--text)}.no-data-message{text-align:center;padding:40px 20px;color:var(--text-dim);font-size:16px}.cell-menu-overlay{display:none;position:fixed;inset:0;background:rgba(0,0,0,.8);z-index:450;align-items:center;justify-content:center}.cell-menu-overlay.show{display:flex}.cell-menu{background:var(--surface);border-radius:20px;padding:20px;width:280px;border:1px solid var(--border);display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:10px}.cell-menu-title{font-size:16px;font-weight:600;text-align:center;margin-bottom:6px}.cell-menu-sub{font-size:13px;color:var(--text-dim);text-align:center;margin-top:-6px;margin-bottom:6px}.cell-menu-btn{padding:12px;border-radius:10px;font-weight:600;font-size:15px;cursor:pointer;border:1px solid var(--border);background:var(--surface2);color:var(--text)}.cell-menu-btn.danger{background:rgba(239,68,68,.12);border-color:rgba(239,68,68,.4);color:#f87171}.cell-menu-btn.cancel{background:0 0;border:none;color:var(--text-dim)}.cell-menu-btn:disabled{opacity:.35;cursor:default}.cell-menu-btn.active{border-color:var(--accent-on)}.cell-menu-textarea{width:100%;min-height:80px;padding:10px;border-radius:10px;border:1px solid var(--border);background:var(--surface2);color:var(--text);font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:12px;resize:vertical;box-sizing:border-box}.day-cell.pasted{outline:1px dashed var(--highlight-pasted);outline-offset:1px}.day-cell.edited{outline:1px dashed var(--highlight-edited);outline-offset:1px}.cell-menu-anchor{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;padding:8px 4px;font-size:14px;color:var(--text-dim);cursor:pointer}.cell-menu-anchor input[type=checkbox]{width:18px;height:18px;accent-color:var(--accent-off);cursor:pointer}</style></head><body><header><div class="header-top"><span class="file-info" id="fileInfo" oncontextmenu="return false">Файл не завантажено</span><button class="save-btn" id="saveBtn" onclick="showFormatDialog()" title="Зберегти файл">💾</button><button class="file-btn" title="Відкрити файл" onclick="document.getElementById('fileInput').click()">📂</button><input type="file" id="fileInput" accept=".txt,.lc,text/plain,application/octet-stream" onchange="loadFile(this)"></div><div class="nav-row"><button class="nav-btn" onclick="navBtnClick(-1)">‹</button><div class="month-label" id="monthLabel" onclick="monthLabelClick()">—</div><button class="nav-btn" onclick="navBtnClick(1)">›</button><div class="nav-spacer"></div><div class="ch-btns" id="chBtns" style="display:none"><button class="ch-btn active" id="btnK1" onclick="setChannel(0)">К1</button><button class="ch-btn" id="btnK2" onclick="setChannel(1)">К2</button></div><div class="dst-spacer"></div><button class="dst-btn" id="btnDST" onclick="toggleDST()" title="Літній/Зимовий час">❄️</button></div><div class="weekdays"><div class="weekday">Пн</div><div class="weekday">Вт</div><div class="weekday">Ср</div><div class="weekday">Чт</div><div class="weekday">Пт</div><div class="weekday">Сб</div><div class="weekday">Нд</div></div></header><div id="mainContent"><div class="empty-state"><div class="empty-icon">🌙</div><div class="empty-title">Календар освітлення + </div><div class="empty-sub">Завантажте .lc або .txt файл щоб побачити розклад</div><button class="upload-big-btn" onclick="document.getElementById('fileInput').click()">📂 Відкрити файл</button></div></div><div class="modal-overlay" id="modalOverlay" onclick="closeModal(event)"><div class="modal"><div class="modal-handle"></div><div class="modal-title" id="modalTitle"></div><div class="modal-events-scroll" id="modalEventsContainer"><div id="modalEvents"></div><div id="editSection" style="display:none;"></div></div><div class="modal-buttons-row"><button class="modal-close